			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "1) Open debugbook\r\n2) Got to Region\r\n3) Act 3\r\n4) Wyrm's Crossing\r\n5) Refugee Camp\r\n6.0) oe OIStartOrinFlamingFist to start the dialog (do the other steps below first if you want them enabled)\r\n6.1) oe OIEnableOrinFlamingFist to enable journal as Orin\r\n6.2) oe OIMetOrinOnce to enable that you've met Orin in previous impersonation."
				},
