				],
				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "|Standing quietly behind the Big Barn, Rowan is just trying to do his job and maybe avoid getting too involved with the refugees and locals that are making a fuss on the other side of the building.  He’s not the most courageous, and certainly not hard-working, but his job isn’t exactly fascinating right now. |"
